name: Gin And Tonic
prepTime: 2 minutes
cookTime: 0 minutes
portions: 1

ingredients:
  - (3/2 oz)   Gin
  - (1 Splash) Tonic Water
  - (3 slices) Cucumber
  - (1 sprig)  Rosemary

steps:
  - Muddle two thin slices of cucumber in a lowball glass
  - Fill glass halfway with crushed ice
  - Pour in Gin, fill with tonic and stir a bit
  - Add thick cucumber slice to rim and drop in rosemary sprig for garnish
